Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.370 --> 00:00:02.680
We start by right-clicking 
on our package name

00:00:02.680 --> 00:00:03.830
to create the new activity

00:00:03.830 --> 00:00:06.600
from the Blank Activity 
with Fragment template.

00:00:07.270 --> 00:00:10.060
So for Name, we use DetailActivity,

00:00:11.390 --> 00:00:14.206
and again, the hierarchical
parent of this class

00:00:14.206 --> 00:00:16.842
is going to be our MainActivity.

00:00:17.322 --> 00:00:19.020
So as you can see,

00:00:19.020 --> 00:00:21.590
we now have a new DetailActivity

00:00:21.590 --> 00:00:24.950
along with the XML for activity_detail.

00:00:24.950 --> 00:00:27.470
And, a fragment associated
with that activity.

00:00:27.973 --> 00:00:29.455
Great! You're done.

00:00:29.855 --> 00:00:32.368
But we still aren't launching
our new activity.

